mentions.context: For this experiment, the classifier is the RandomForestClassifier (and we had the same results with the other classifiers).
The classification algorithms are borrowed from the sklearn library [20].

Then, the next season prediction problem consists in learning a probabilistic classifier (Naive-Bayes classifier, logistic regression, decision tree or random forests) or a time series classifiers (TSForest [16], Rocket [17]).
